    <item>
      <title>解析“美国优先”交易如何席卷华尔街</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/how-america-first-trades-have-swept-wall-street-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫为他长达十年的投资战略增添了新的弹药，这一战略呼应了他 2016 年策略的“让美国再次伟大”口号。美国优先贸易——购买在美国表现优于世界其他国家时获胜的资产——周三获得了强大的推动力，因为人们押注共和党胜利者将推出刺激国内增长并使世界最大经济体免受海外竞争的政策。开场贸易主播克里蒂古普塔与斯蒂芬卡罗尔和汤姆麦肯齐一起在彭博电台进行讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/how-america-first-trades-have-swept-wall-street-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:55:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨执政联盟解散推动德国股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/german-stocks-lifted-by-demise-of-scholz-s-fractious-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国股市周四大幅上涨，原因是该国不受欢迎的联合政府开始瓦解，引发人们对明年提前选举将带来急需的经济增长的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/german-stocks-lifted-by-demise-of-scholz-s-fractious-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:52:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴克莱：欧元兑美元汇率尚未完全持平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/barclays-sees-euro-dollar-falling-to-1-03-but-not-parity-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱外汇策略副总裁斯凯拉·蒙哥马利·科宁 (Skylar Montgomery Koning) 研究了欧元兑美元的走弱情况，她的公司认为，由于唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 第二届政府的关税预期以及可能最终推动欧元兑美元平价的因素，欧元兑美元汇率将跌至 1.03 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-07/barclays-sees-euro-dollar-falling-to-1-03-but-not-parity-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:44:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Evercore 称美国股市牛市才刚刚开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/the-bull-market-in-us-stocks-is-just-starting-evercore-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Evercore ISI 策略师表示，美国股市上涨势头远未结束，他们认为唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的简化程序计划将推动标准普尔 500 指数到明年年中再上涨 11%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/the-bull-market-in-us-stocks-is-just-starting-evercore-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国即将举行提前投票，能源目标面临阻碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-looming-snap-vote-throws-wrench-into-energy-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近年来，高昂的能源成本和向清洁燃料转型的不确定性是德国工业巨头外流的主要原因。执政联盟的突然解散和迫在眉睫的提前选举将使这一问题更加难以解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-looming-snap-vote-throws-wrench-into-energy-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行降息并警告预算通胀压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/boe-delivers-rate-cut-with-warning-of-budget-s-inflation-impact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行今年第二次下调借贷成本，但没有暗示将加快宽松政策，并警告称预算可能导致通胀上升多达半个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/boe-delivers-rate-cut-with-warning-of-budget-s-inflation-impact</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡特朗普的影响，大选震动后油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡唐纳德·特朗普的大选胜利对原油市场可能产生的影响，美元停止了大选后的上涨，油价在周三经历了过山车式波动后出现下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走软，股市守住特朗普大选涨势：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员继续关注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫以及这对美联储利率路径的影响，美国股指期货维持了选举日后的涨幅，美元走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
